K \times K
 \Lambda_{K} = \left(   \begin{array}{ccccc}     2 & -1 & 0 & \cdots & 0 \\     -1 & 2 & -1 & \cdots & 0 \\    0 & -1 & \ddots & \ddots & \vdots \\     \vdots & \ddots & \ddots & \ddots & -1 \\     0 & 0 & \ldots & -1 & 2 \\   \end{array}\right). 
